      <p>Features may be added, changed, or removed at any time.</p>
      <p>We may perform maintenance without prior notice.</p>
      <p>We are not responsible for losses caused by downtime or temporary unavailability.</p>

      <h2>12. Open Source</h2>
      <p>The RTS source code is released under the GNU Affero General Public License (AGPL), unless stated otherwise.</p>
