      <p>Anyone running their own copy of the software is responsible for their own rules, policies, and legal documents.</p>
      <p>Contributions submitted to the project remain subject to the repository license.</p>

      <h2>13. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>RTS is provided "as is" and "as available."</p>
      <p>
        While we work to keep the information on RTS accurate and useful, we do not guarantee that every website, review, or piece of
        content is complete, accurate, safe, or up to date.
      </p>
      <p>Users are responsible for evaluating the information they choose to rely on.</p>
      <p>
        Links to third-party websites are provided for convenience. We do not own or control those websites and are not responsible for
        their content, security, privacy practices, or availability.
      </p>

      <h2>14. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
