        consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Service.
      </p>
      <p>This includes, but is not limited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>loss of data;</li>
        <li>loss of profits;</li>
        <li>business interruption;</li>
        <li>security incidents caused by third-party services;</li>
        <li>loss resulting from inaccurate user-generated content;</li>
        <li>temporary or permanent unavailability of the Service.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Nothing in these Terms limits liability where such limitation is prohibited by applicable law.</p>
      <p>This includes decisions you make based on information published on RTS.</p>

      <h2>15. Privacy</h2>
      <p>Your privacy matters.</p>
      <p>Our collection and use of personal information is explained in our Privacy Policy.</p>
      <p>By using RTS, you acknowledge that your personal information will be processed as described in the Privacy Policy.</p>

      <h2>16. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>RTS will continue to grow, and these Terms may change over time.</p>
      <p>
        If we make significant changes, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We may also notify registered users
        through the website or by email when appropriate.
      </p>
      <p>By continuing to use RTS after updated Terms take effect, you agree to the revised version.</p>
      <p>If you do not agree with the updated Terms, you should stop using the Service.</p>

      <h2>17. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Finland.</p>
      <p>
        Where applicable, the rights and protections provided under the laws of the European Union, including the General Data Protection
        Regulation (GDPR), continue to apply.
      </p>
      <p>If any part of these Terms is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining sections remain in effect.</p>

      <h2>18. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms, copyright matters, privacy, moderation, or legal requests should be sent to:</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:admin@readthisshit.fyi">admin@readthisshit.fyi</a></p>
      <p>
        GitHub Repository: <a href="https://github.com/readthisshit-fyi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >https://github.com/readthisshit-fyi</a
        >
      </p>
      <p>Bug reports and feature requests are welcome through the GitHub repository.</p>

      <h2>19. Thank You</h2>
      <p>RTS is an open source project built by people who care about making the web easier to explore.</p>
      <p>Thank you for helping keep the community useful, respectful, and welcoming for everyone.</p>
